=head1 DESCRIPTION

Indicates the Amazon CloudWatch alarm detected while running an
assessment.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AlarmArn => Str

Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Amazon CloudWatch alarm.


=head2 Source => Str

Indicates the source of the Amazon CloudWatch alarm. That is, it
indicates if the alarm was created using Resilience Hub recommendation
(C<AwsResilienceHub>), or if you had created the alarm in Amazon
CloudWatch (C<Customer>).



